Ready to wear womenswear brand 2207 is a solid favourite of a lot of our style stars and recently we found two of them in this best-selling piece. Today’s BN Pick Your Fave features African superstar Tiwa Savage and the Baby Girl herself Toke Makinwa in this of the moment tie-dye, bow detail 2207byTBally skirt. <img src="https://i2.wp.com/www.bellanaijastyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/linda-2207bytbally-C2C-PYF-1.png?ssl=1" data-recalc-dims="1" />

Singer Tiwa Savage styled the green and blue 2207 by TBally skirt with a white peasant style crop top, white sneakers and diamante hoops. She completed the Romani feel of the look with a silk scarf of a similar palette and a fresh faced makeup look. <img src="https://i1.wp.com/www.bellanaijastyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/103140798_146018943681415_9007563541105739832_n-e1592413173852.jpg?ssl=1" data-recalc-dims="1" />The ever stylish social media maven Toke Makinwa on the other hand wore her 2207 skirt with a sheer mesh turtleneck with the ‘Baby Girl’ logo emblazoned on it. She opted for a high ponytail and accessorised with Gucci sneakers and a chainstrap bag and finished off the look with silver hoops. <img src="https://i0.wp.com/www.bellanaijastyle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/103351324_257734592336943_4932838222906481175_n.jpg?ssl=1" data-recalc-dims="1" />Both women are most definitely stunners in this 2207 by TBally skirt but whose styling do you prefer? The post BN Pick Your Fave | Toke Makinwa and Tiwa Savage In 2207 By TBally appeared first on BellaNaija – Showcasing Africa to the world. Read today!. Original Article Get all the Latest news, Breaking headlines,Sport, Education, Finance, Gists, Jobs, Music/Video, Technology and Top stories in real time in Nigeria and around the world.